                <button type="button" class="quick-question text-left text-xs text-accent/90 bg-accent-bg/50 hover:bg-accent-bg border border-accent/15 hover:border-accent/30 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 transition-all cursor-pointer" data-question="sv_cheats 会影响哪些类型的指令？">sv_cheats 会影响哪些类型的指令？</button>
